            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How we marvel at this mercy"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So far-reaching and so vast!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It has reached us, e’en the sinners,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And will ever hold us fast."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "From this mercy, from this mercy,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What can cause us to be cast?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For Thy mercy we are grateful,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "’Tis so rich, so plenteous!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thru Thy mercy in redemption,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thou hast richly favored us."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If without this, if without this,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How could we be favored thus?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, Thy mercy, so inspiring!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Gentle, tender, dear and sweet!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "With Thy patience and Thy kindness,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Us in all our need it meets."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It we treasure, it we treasure,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nothing can with it compete."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Father, we enjoy Thy mercy,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ever fresh and ever new;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Every morning shed upon us,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It refreshes as the dew."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How we taste it! how we taste it!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Giving Thee the praises due."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We can never cease to praise Thee,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As Thy mercy e’er endures;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All Thy grace and all Thy favor,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ever for us it secures."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Trusting in it, trusting in it,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy sure mercy us assures."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    }
  ],
